   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern ist es sehr klug, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das so zu machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Sache stimmt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.280", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber darum haben wir uns doch gemeinsam gek\u00fcmmert: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die IKB hatte deshalb ein Problem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie im Ausland Dinge getan hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Deutschland gar nicht erlaubt gewesen w\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.640", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gesch\u00e4fte mit tranchierten Verbriefungen sind in Irland erfolgt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.680", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re in der Form in Deutschland gar nicht m\u00f6glich gewesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das war das Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten die BaFin eingeladen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber die hat uns erkl\u00e4rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.680", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen alles pr\u00fcfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nur bis zur Grenze der deutschen Jurisdiktion. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen nicht in Irland pr\u00fcfen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.600", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war der Hintergrund. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum haben wir uns jetzt gek\u00fcmmert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
